de.gbv.beacon
Class BeaconBuilder

java.lang.Object
  de.gbv.beacon.BeaconBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
BeaconProcessor
public class BeaconBuilder
extends Object
implements BeaconProcessor

Expand links, etc. This class receives and validates raw meta fields and link fields from a serialized Beacon dump, constructs full Beacon links (BeaconLink), and calls the method of a BeaconHandler to handle the result. Applications should not directly use this class but implement a BeaconHandler to receive fully expanded links.

See Also:
BeaconHandler, BeaconParser
